Note:
runatime/integration/system_interface/environment_manager.runa
Environment Variable Management System

This module provides comprehensive environment variable management including:
- System environment variable access and modification
- Process-specific environment isolation and inheritance
- Environment variable validation and type conversion
- Secure environment variable handling with access control
- Environment variable persistence and restoration
- Cross-platform environment variable abstraction
- Environment variable expansion and interpolation
- Configuration management through environment variables
- Environment-based application configuration
- Dynamic environment variable updates during runtime
- Environment variable caching for performance optimization
- Integration with process creation and management
- Environment variable debugging and inspection tools
- Template-based environment configuration management
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

Note: =====================================================================
Note: ENVIRONMENT MANAGEMENT DATA STRUCTURES
Note: =====================================================================

Type called "EnvironmentVariable":
    name as String
    value as String
    source as String
    is_system_variable as Boolean
    is_read_only as Boolean
    is_sensitive as Boolean
    validation_pattern as String
    default_value as String
    last_modified_timestamp as Integer
    access_count as Integer

Type called "EnvironmentScope":
    scope_name as String
    scope_type as String
    parent_scope as String
    variables as Dictionary[String, EnvironmentVariable]
    inheritance_enabled as Boolean
    isolation_level as String
    modification_permissions as List[String]
    creation_timestamp as Integer

Type called "EnvironmentTemplate":
    template_name as String
    template_description as String
    required_variables as List[String]
    optional_variables as List[String]
    variable_defaults as Dictionary[String, String]
    validation_rules as Dictionary[String, String]
    expansion_rules as Dictionary[String, String]

Type called "EnvironmentManager":
    active_scopes as Dictionary[String, EnvironmentScope]
    system_environment as Dictionary[String, EnvironmentVariable]
    cached_values as Dictionary[String, String]
    access_permissions as Dictionary[String, List[String]]
    modification_history as List[Dictionary[String, String]]
    templates as Dictionary[String, EnvironmentTemplate]

